{"tid":1386720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發假誓要落地獄] 本人謹以至誠作出宣言","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:52:19.000Z","uid":218313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3df3700cf82051f95161ee59acd3940a562fd4c8","tid":1386720,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩搵返警隊誓詞出黎<br />\n睇返真係貽笑大方<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>警隊誓詞</strong><br />\n本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切合法命令。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不畏懼</strong></span><br />\n- 一見到白衫就調頭走<br />\n- 警犬爆炸抱頭走.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不徇私</strong></span><br />\n- 包庇鄉黑, 同胞施暴<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人</span></strong><br />\n- 敵視一切黑衫, 黃絲<br />\n- 以headshot 前線義士為樂<br />\n- 係香港帶個口罩都唔得<br />\n- 全部示威既都應該死<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">合法命令</span></strong><br />\n- 棍棍扑頭, 下下headshot<br />\n- 執行職務唔駛委任證<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 任何宗教都有講發假誓既懲罰, 我敢話,呢班人死左之後一定落地獄</span></span>"},{"pid":"2142d57e3ef60f7bc98083e5772ab9e448ee858b","tid":1386720,"uid":196114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"落撚硬！"},{"pid":"ce1307589f2ad58b9553b095a3a59dd8b81da3a4","tid":1386720,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"仆佢地個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}